<Layout title="All Destinations" description="AIMS Travel destinations — Africa, Asia, Europe, the Americas, and the Middle East. Group tours to over 30 countries worldwide.">

  <div class="hero-band">
    <h1>All Destinations</h1>
    <p>Group tours to over 30 countries worldwide</p>
  </div>

  <main>
    <h1>AIMS Travel Destination Catalog</h1>

    <p>
      AIMS Travel operated group tour programs across six continents, crafting itineraries that balanced world-famous landmarks with genuine cultural encounters. Below you will find the complete catalog of regional programs and individual tour offerings. Each regional page includes detailed destination descriptions, itinerary highlights, and practical travel information.
    </p>

    <div class="dest-grid">
      <a href="/destinations/africa" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Africa</h3>
        <p>South Africa, Kenya &amp; Tanzania Safari, Botswana, Namibia</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/asia" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Asia &amp; the Orient</h3>
        <p>China &amp; Yangtze River, India, Vietnam &amp; Cambodia, Thailand</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/europe" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Europe</h3>
        <p>Greece, Central Europe, Russia, Scandinavia, Sicily, Croatia</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/americas" class="dest-card">
        <h3>The Americas</h3>
        <p>Peru &amp; Machu Picchu, Ecuador &amp; Galapagos, Costa Rica, Cuba, Antarctica</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/middle-east" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Middle East</h3>
        <p>Egypt &amp; the Nile, Turkey, Israel, Mediterranean</p>
      </a>
    </div>

